msgstr "這些限制通常由硬件定義，並由亮度系統返回。"

msgid ""
"These parameters are sourced from the system’s high-level graphics layer. "
"Because the display is ultimately composed through CoreAnimation and "
"backboardd before it reaches the screen hardware, the values shown here are "
"estimates and may not precisely reflect the true behavior of the physical "
