msgid "Gas Gauge (Basic)"
msgstr "電量監測計（基本）"

msgid ""
"All Gas Gauge metrics are dynamically retrieved from the onboard sensor "
"array in real time. Should anomalies be detected in specific readings, this "
"may indicate the presence of unauthorized components or require diagnostics "
"through Apple Authorised Service Provider."
msgstr ""
"本設備所有電量監測計（Gas Gauge）數據均實時讀取自內置傳感器系統。若您發現部分"
"數值存在異常，則可能涉及未經認證的組件、集成或設備傳感單元。如果需要檢測。建"
"議通過 Apple 認證服務渠道進行專業診斷。"

msgid "Device Name"
msgstr "設備名稱"

msgid ""
"This indicates the name of the current Gas Gauge IC used by the installed "
"battery."
msgstr "當前電池使用的電量監測計芯片的名稱。"

msgid "Health"
msgstr "電池健康"

msgid "SoC"
msgstr "電池餘量"

msgid "Avg. Temperature"
msgstr "平均溫度"

msgid "Charging"
msgstr "正在充電"

msgid "Full Charge Capacity"
msgstr "滿充容量"

msgid "Designed Capacity"
msgstr "設計容量"

msgid "Battery Uptime"
msgstr "電池運行時長"

msgid "The length of time the Battery Management System (BMS) has been up."
msgstr "從電池管理系統啓動開始的時長。"

msgid "Qmax"
msgstr "最大化學容量"

msgid ""
"Chemical depth of discharge recorded at the most recent qualifying open-"
"circuit-voltage reading while the battery was relaxed. The gas gauge reports "
"DOD₀ on a raw 0–16384 scale; Battman displays it as a percentage. This "
"reference value may not equal the battery's present depth of discharge."
msgstr ""
"電池處於靜置狀態時，在最近一次符合條件的開路電壓讀數中記錄的化學放電深度。電量計以 "
"0–16384 的原始範圍回報 DOD₀；Battman 將其顯示為百分比。此參考值可能與電池目前的放電深度不同。"

msgid "Passed Charge"
msgstr "通過電量"

msgid ""
"Signed charge passed through the sense resistor since the last Impedance "
"Track simulation/DOD₀ reference update. This is not lifetime charge "
"throughput or the battery cycle count."
msgstr ""
"自上次 Impedance Track 模擬/DOD₀ 參考值更新以來，通過電流感測電阻的有符號電荷量。"
"這不是電池壽命期間的累計電荷吞吐量，也不是電池循環計數。"

msgid "Voltage"
msgstr "電壓"

msgid "Avg. Current"
msgstr "平均電流"

msgid "Avg. Power"
msgstr "平均功率"

msgid "Cell Count"
msgstr "電芯數量"

msgid "Designed Cycle Count"
msgstr "設計循環次數"

msgid "State of Charge"
msgstr "充電狀態"

msgid "State of Charge (UI)"
msgstr "充電狀態（UI）"

msgid ""
"The \"Battery Percentage\" displayed exactly on your status bar. This is the "
"SoC that Apple wants to tell you."
msgstr "狀態欄上所顯示的「電量百分比」，是 Apple 想讓用戶知道的「充電狀態」。"

msgid "Resistance Scale"
msgstr "阻抗系數"

msgid "Battery Serial No."
msgstr "電池序列號"

msgid "Chemistry ID"
msgstr "化合物ID"

msgid ""
"Chemistry unique identifier (ChemID) assigned to each battery in Texas "
"Instruments' database. It ensures accurate calculations and predictions."
msgstr ""
"化合物ID（ChemID）是德州儀器數據庫中為每個電池配置分配的唯一標識符，其可確保"
"準確的計算和預測。"

msgid "Flags"
msgstr "標示位"

msgid "True Remaining Capacity"
msgstr "真實剩餘容量"

msgid "OCV Current"
msgstr "開路電流"

msgid "OCV Voltage"
msgstr "開路電壓"

msgid "Max Load Current"
msgstr "最大負荷電流"

msgid "Max Load Current 2"
msgstr "最大負荷電流2"

msgid "IT Misc Status"
msgstr "IT 雜項數據"

msgid ""
"This field refers to the miscellaneous data returned by battery Impedance "
"Track™ Gas Gauge IC."
msgstr "此項指電池的 Impedance Track™ 所返回的電量監測計雜項數據。"

msgid "Simulation Rate"
msgstr "模擬頻率"

msgid ""
"This field refers to the rate of Gas Gauge performing Impedance Track™ "
"simulations."
msgstr "此項指電量監測計執行 Impedance Track™ 模擬的頻率。"

msgid "Daily Max SoC"
msgstr "單日最大餘量"

msgid "Daily Min SoC"
msgstr "單日最小餘量"

msgid "Adapter Details"
msgstr "適配器信息"

msgid ""
"All adapter information is dynamically retrieved from the hardware of the "
"currently connected adapter (or cable if you are using Lightning ports). If "
"any of the data is missing, it may indicate that the power source is not "
"providing the relevant information, or there may be a hardware issue with "
"the power source."
msgstr ""
"所有電源適配器信息均來源於當前設備連接的電源適配器硬件（或者 Lightning 數據"
"線）。如果其中任何一項信息為空，可能意味著所連接的電源未提供相關數據，或電源"
"可能存在硬件故障。"

msgid "Port"
msgstr "端口"

msgid ""
"Port of currently connected adapter. On macOS, this is the USB port that the "
"adapter currently attached."
msgstr "已連接的適配器所在的端口，在 macOS 中，表示當前所連接的 USB 端口。"

msgid "Adapter Type"
msgstr "適配器類型"

msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr "兼容性"

msgid ""
"This field refers to the Family Code (kIOPSPowerAdapterFamilyKey) of "
"currently connected power adapter."
msgstr "此參數表示當前電源適配器的「類型代碼」（kIOPSPowerAdapterFamilyKey）。"

msgid "Reason"
msgstr "原因"

msgid ""
"If this field appears in the list, it indicates that an issue has occurred "
"or that a condition was met, causing charging to stop."
msgstr ""
"當此項出現在列表中時，表示發生了問題或滿足了某個條件，從而導致充電停止。"

msgid "Current Rating"
msgstr "額定電流"

msgid ""
"Current rating of connected power source, this does not indicates the real-"
"time passing current."
msgstr "當前電源的額定電流，此參數不表示實時輸入電流。"

msgid "Voltage Rating"
msgstr "額定電壓"

msgid ""
"Voltage rating of connected power source, this does not indicates the real-"
"time passing voltage."
msgstr "當前電源的額定電壓，此參數不表示實時輸入電壓。"

msgid "Input Current"
msgstr "輸入電流"

msgid "Real-time input current (IBUS) from the connected power source."
msgstr "已連接電源的實時輸入電流（IBUS）。"

msgid "Input Voltage"
msgstr "輸入電壓"

msgid "Real-time input voltage (VBUS) from the connected power source."
msgstr "已連接電源的實時輸入電壓（VBUS）。"

msgid "Charging Current"
msgstr "充電電流"

msgid "The real-time passing current to internal battery."
msgstr "設備電池的實時輸入電流。"

msgid "Charging Voltage"
msgstr "充電電壓"

msgid "The real-time passing voltage to internal battery."
msgstr "設備電池的實時輸入電壓。"

msgid "Charger IC ID"
msgstr "充電芯片ID"

msgid "Model Name"
